&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE ROLE:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a Pharmacist, Formulary &amp;amp; Clinical Strategy to join Rightway&#39;s growing Clinical Strategy team. This is an early-career role designed for a clinical pharmacist who is ready to apply their managed care expertise in a technology-forward, fast-paced environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will support the design, maintenance, and optimization of Rightway&#39;s formularies and prior authorization (PA) criteria, while also contributing to data-informed recommendations that shape our clinical strategy. Critically, this role is for someone who is not just comfortable with AI tools — but actively uses them to work smarter, move faster, and surface better insights.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role reports to the leader of Clinical Strategy and works cross-functionally with Product, Data &amp;amp; Insights, Cost of Goods, and Client Operations.&lt;/p&gt;
