&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE ROLE:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Under the general supervision of the Clinical Lead, the Telehealth Triage (RN) performs clinical triage, condition support, care planning, clinical education, and care coordination functions in supporting Rightway members with navigating, accessing, and best managing their care needs.&amp;nbsp; The Telehealth Triage (RN) also serves as a trusted advisor for appropriately directing care to high-quality providers with the objective of improving clinical outcomes while also reducing healthcare costs e.g. minimizing ED or other unnecessary care visits while increasing utilization of more appropriate care settings, such as primary care doctors.&lt;/p&gt;
